freenet.node
Class PeerNodeStatus

java.lang.Object
  freenet.node.PeerNodeStatus
Direct Known Subclasses:
DarknetPeerNodeStatus, OpennetPeerNodeStatus
public class PeerNodeStatus
extends Object

Contains various status information for a PeerNode. Used e.g. in DarknetConnectionsToadlet to reduce race-conditions while creating the page.

Version:
$Id$
Author:
David 'Bombe' Roden <bombe@freenetproject.org>
